    "attributes": {
        "action": "Restart issuing oil and gas licenses in the North Sea",
        "additional_details": "We believe the North Sea oil and gas fields are a major part of our economy, and that the drive to net zero is making us colder and poorer. Until we have what we feel is a viable and cost effective alternative in place to oil and gas, we think we should make the most of the resources we have.",
        "background": "I would like the Government to reverse the policy of not issuing new contracts to search for and extract oil and gas in the North Sea and British waters.",
